    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《命运之前》：时空的奇点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《命运之前》将复古科幻元素与富有想象力的漫画艺术相结合，为您带来独特的生存冒险体验。穿越传送门，探索不同时空，收集资源，应对生存挑战，深入神秘的地下城，并逐步揭开末日虫灾背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跃迁时空</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索从荒凉沙漠到神秘森林的多元环境，每个时空背后都藏着未知的挑战和奇迹。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/e5ca2fb28db233ab648612b6d5b12f95.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/e5ca2fb28db233ab648612b6d5b12f95.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/e5ca2fb28db233ab648612b6d5b12f95.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度剧情</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追踪克罗诺宝石的神秘踪迹，与奥德研究所的科学家一起，解锁时空深处的谜题，阻止灾难的发生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a526eced9293a34d386ffaa1743cf631.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a526eced9293a34d386ffaa1743cf631.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a526eced9293a34d386ffaa1743cf631.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备丰富</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过一百种武器与众多独特道具，塑造个性化的战斗风格，赋予每次探险独一无二的色彩。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/6c3fd266f805d8f41e5cf24f287c387a.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/6c3fd266f805d8f41e5cf24f287c387a.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/6c3fd266f805d8f41e5cf24f287c387a.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜挑战</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合直观的操作界面与环境互动，每一个谜题都是对智慧的磨砺。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/42c62e580b536678bb88b84514645ff8.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/42c62e580b536678bb88b84514645ff8.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/42c62e580b536678bb88b84514645ff8.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵感之作</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一帧都是对经典的现代再现，向墨比斯等艺术大师致敬。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/5833d4a603570bce570f7d4b2c562670.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/5833d4a603570bce570f7d4b2c562670.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/5833d4a603570bce570f7d4b2c562670.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美术风格</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古与现代的融合 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70、80年代科幻背景与漫画风格相结合，每个像素都散发着复古科幻的魅力。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘世界 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心绘制的场景与角色，展现出一个充满生机与想象的多彩世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a227b751100ad78f54236c48f3b5ec56.poster.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a227b751100ad78f54236c48f3b5ec56.webm?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/a227b751100ad78f54236c48f3b5ec56.mp4?t=1769139219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情概览</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“在时间和空间的交汇点，隐藏着无限的可能性与希望。它们如同瞬间的流星，短暂而耀眼。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在机器人与人类共存的年代，一颗陨石的降临预示着即将到来的灾难。作为科学家伊恩·斯图尔特，与奥德团队的领航者亚伯·莫里森一同，深入时空的奇迹中，探索、战斗，并揭开时空的神秘面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/2de4e7b4b25477b3923396c301fdffd4.avif?t=1769139219\" width=600 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越时空的帷幕，探索无尽的可能性，让《命运之前》成为您的时空之旅。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入我们，一起探索《命运之前》的世界！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/bec0721b37b8c5c198351b9ef1efdfc1.avif?t=1769139219\" width=601 height=127 /></span></p>",
